title: Tokak PPVRip
description:
Release Date: 20 Jun 2013

Language:Malay

Genre:Action

Running Time: 90 minutes

Director:Sabree Fadzil

Cast:Mikail Andre, Diana Johor


A horror film about an incident at a secluded resort that takes place over the course of one night. The Tokak is a vengeful spirit from Sungai Raya who has possessed a man named Iskandar, owner of the resort. In order for Iskandar to return to a human, he has to murder and drink the blood of six women who have sinned with lust in one night.
